criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age over 18;

          -  Diagnosed with breast cancer and submitted to surgical treatment, regardless of the
             type of surgery;

          -  With up to 24 months post-operatively, already completed cycles of adjuvant therapies
             (radiotherapy and/or chemotherapy);

          -  Moderate functional disability with a minimum score of 30% QuickDash questionnaire;

          -  Impaired quality of life;

          -  Able to understand and access mobile applications or live with someone who assists,
             has internet access and telephone contact.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  open lesions;

          -  acquired infections;

          -  chronic disease or previous motor sequelae that would interfere with participation in
             the study;

          -  women who have difficulty understanding the questions or questionnaires applied or
             proposed activities;

          -  diagnosis of lymphedema;

          -  have no functional alterations in the upper limbs or quality of life.
